        style="background-color: #fff;border-radius: 2px;padding: 1rem; text-align: center;font-size: 1.15rem;margin-top: 0.75rem;"
      ><p style="color:black;font-size: 1.25rem">We're glad to have you join
          <b>PicPocket!</b>
        </p>
